It's an even break for a while . 
But once he gets that information he's looking for , then look out . 
You and Olaf and I are the wolves and the flies and the midges again and the strafing will be about due . 
Nevertheless , with three to one against him , if he can get away with it he deserves to . 
I'm for taking him up , if you are . 
There was almost a twinkle in Marakinoff's eyes . 
