Nevertheless , I'll just keep the guns . 
And now , he said , I will tell you what I know . 
I found the secret of the door mechanism even as you did , Dr . 
But by carelessness , my condensers were broken . 
I was forced to wait while I sent for others and the waiting might be for months . 
I took certain precautions , and on the first night of this full moon I hid myself within the vault of Chau ta leur . 
An involuntary thrill of admiration for the man went through me at the manifest heroism of this leap in the dark . 
I could see it reflected in Larry's face . 
