We follow Golden Eyes , he said to me . 
Follow ? I echoed stupidly . 
At our right , a few feet away , the passage ended abruptly in a square of polished stone , from which came faint rose radiance . 
The roof of the place was less than two feet over O'Keefe's head . 
Olaf beside him , he strode to the wall and peered over . 
