What you see down there are people JUST PLAIN PEOPLE . 
And wherever there's people is where I live . 
Get me ? There's no way in but in and no way out but out , said O'Keefe . 
Eggs are eggs no matter how they're cooked and people are just people , fellow travellers , no matter what dish they are in , he concluded . 
Come on ! With the three of us close behind him , he marched toward the entrance . 
CHAPTER XIII Yolara , Priestess of the Shining One YOU'D better have this handy , Doc . 
