Her blue eyes flashed triumphantly her chiming laughter rang . 
Yolara swayed close alluring , tempting . 
He arose , face all reckless gaiety rollick ing deviltry . 
But the contempt in his action they did recog nize and a dead , a fearful silence fell upon them all . 
Lu gur's eyes blazed , little sparks of crimson in their green . 
