And why don't you get rid of that devilish pet of yours , and be good ! She looked at him , puzzled , Marakinoff leaned over , trans lated to Lugur . 
The red dwarf smiled maliciously , drew near the priestess whispered to her what was without doubt as near as he could come in the Murian to Larry's own very colloquial phrases . 
Hear me , Lakla ! she cried . 
