Still smiling , I sank at once into sleep . 
How long I slumbered I do not know . 
A low and thunder ous booming coming through the deep window slit , reverbe rated through the room and awakened me . 
Sounds as though the bass drums of every jazz band in New York were serenading us ! he observed . 
